name: HEYLO!
description:
We come with our original idea to express our opinion through artworks. the story is represented mostly by characters in cyborg body in every single scene. We called it cybro-G project, made by two brothers who want to having fun with their imagination to express their opinion. See you at Cybro-G world!

this is the 1st scene that we drop to begin our journey. introducing "Cyru" (the fox-cyborg character) hi-jacking the train and holding a bottle of spray paint.

This illustration describing me and my brother @sidvizeus ‘s goals in NFT project, where we are not only create a mark with our artwork, but slow yet consistent we will conquer the train whatever fast it is.
